They denied the offences against them and applied to be freed on bond. 

In the theft case, Mutembei and Shivachi were freed on a cash bail of Sh500,000 each. In the charge of being found with many simcards without a valid reason, the suspects were freed Sh200,000 cash bail each. 

The cases will be mentioned on March 3 for pre-trial directions. 

